{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_06_01",
  "title": "白石千紗",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さとみによるユニットの",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "メンバーが決まって数日後",
      "startTime": 1.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私って子供っぽいでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 3.5999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどうしたんだ？　何か言われたのか？",
      "startTime": 7.3333332856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃないんですけど……今回のユニットは\n各グループの最年少が集まってますよね？",
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのすみれちゃん、リズノワのこころちゃん\n月ストのすずちゃん、サニピの雫ちゃん……",
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな年少組のユニットに\nどうして私が選ばれたのかなって思ったんです",
      "startTime": 30.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "年齢なら、琴乃ちゃんや瑠依さん、葵さんも\n私と同い年ですし……",
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "私より年下の優ちゃんや芽衣ちゃんもいるのに\nみんなを差し置いて年少組に交じるなんて……",
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私ってそんなに子供っぽく見えるんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 49.566666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかして千紗は、自分の見た目が）\n（子供っぽいことを気にしているのか？）",
      "startTime": 57.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "前にも似た企画があっただろう？　あの時、千紗は\nお姉さんとしてみんなを支えてくれたじゃないか",
      "startTime": 63.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "見た目のことなんて気にしなくていい\n大切なのは外見より中身だ",
      "startTime": 69.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、{user}さんも\n私の見た目は子供っぽいと思ってるんですね",
      "startTime": 74.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それは……子供っぽいというか……ほら\n童顔で可愛らしいところも千紗の魅力だから……",
      "startTime": 83.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "……意地悪を言ってごめんなさい\n見た目が子供っぽいことは自分でも分かってるんです",
      "startTime": 90.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "誤解しないで下さいね\n可愛いらしいって言われるのが嫌な訳じゃないんです",
      "startTime": 97.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、いつまでも子供っぽいのは\nどうなのかなって思って……",
      "startTime": 104.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗は大人っぽくなりたいのか？",
      "startTime": 107.3999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、内面だけじゃなくて\n見た目や雰囲気も大人っぽくなりたいんです",
      "startTime": 112.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どうしたら大人の雰囲気を出せるんでしょうか\n見当もつかないです……",
      "startTime": 121.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（外見や雰囲気が大人っぽくなる方法か……）\n（確かに、今の千紗には難しいかもしれないな）",
      "startTime": 127.3677520994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 132.666666619,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4313.3333809999785,
          "startTime": 136.98
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666714299992,
          "startTime": 137.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8000.000047699985,
          "startTime": 140.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6466.666714299976,
          "startTime": 139.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.666666619
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.666666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "このマーケットは利回りがレバレッジでロスカットの\nTOBがインサイダー取引……あ、おはようございます",
      "startTime": 138.5050101094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8000070731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗？　一体何をしているんだ？",
      "startTime": 143.8000070731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、株価をチェックしてました",
      "startTime": 146.9333404064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.0333404064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、大人っぽくなりたいって話をしましたよね\nあの後、雫ちゃんに相談してみたんです",
      "startTime": 154.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら雫ちゃんが、星見プロで一番大人っぽい\nスリクスさんを参考にしたらどうかって……",
      "startTime": 162.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.8000070731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それでfranさんの真似をしたのか\nちなみにさっき呟いていたのはどういう意味なんだ？",
      "startTime": 168.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "それは……それっぽい単語を並べただけなので\n私も何が何やら……",
      "startTime": 177.2256736755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.8333404064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか？　大人の雰囲気、出てましたか？",
      "startTime": 179.8333404064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.6333404064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいことは分からなくもないが\nそれは大人っぽいとは違うんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 186.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10044.74188840001,
          "startTime": 196.3114085551
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……\n分かりました、今度は別の方法をやってみます！",
      "startTime": 191.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.8000172456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗？　そこまでして大人っぽく見られたいなんて\nそんなに悩んでいたのか……",
      "startTime": 202.7333435059,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4033.340406400015,
          "startTime": 206.7666839123
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.5166839123
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.5166839123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
